      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 23, United States Code, to compel States to require illuminated signs and other measures on ride-hailing vehicles, to prohibit the sale of such signs, to require ride-hailing companies to implement an electronic access system on ride-hailing vehicles, and to be known as "Sami's Law".</title>
